  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of peanut oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the Thai red curry paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the coconut milk, oat milk, fish sauce, sugar, turmeric, paprika, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened.",
